## Run in Postman Button
[<img src="https://run.pstmn.io/button.svg" alt="Run In Postman" style="width: 128px; height: 32px;">](https://app.getpostman.com/run-collection/51754696-abadd694-4fd7-4ba4-886f-2150bb3eb695?action=collection%2Ffork&source=rip_markdown&collection-url=entityId%3D51754696-abadd694-4fd7-4ba4-886f-2150bb3eb695%26entityType%3Dcollection%26workspaceId%3Df66d949a-9ff9-4f9f-8f62-38f97d6ac87f#?env%5BMilliken%20-%20Movies%20Env%)

Includes valid requests and as well as invalid requests (missing auth, wrong passwords).

Note that you will need to send a POST request to /signup to create the user, then a POST to /signin to log in and recieve a JWT. JWT token will not be in the enviornment.
